high_descs: Approach the coffee table in the living room.
Pick up the gold colored vase from on the coffee table.
Move to the black desk.
Place the gold vase on the desk
Move to the shelves on the right.
Pick up the blue vase on the lower shelf.
Move to the black desk.
Place the blue vase on the desk between the remote and the gold vase.
anns.task_desc: Place two vases on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the glass coffee table.
Pick up the gold vase from the table.
Turn around and go to the black desk.
Place the vase on the black desk.
Turn to the right and locate the shelves on the wall.
Pick up the blue vase from the shelf.
Turn around and go back to the black desk.
Place the blue vase on the black desk.
anns.task_desc: Move two vases to the black desk.

high_descs: Turn around so the open doorway is at your back and move to the coffee table.
Pick up the gold vase from the table.
Carry the vase to the black desk.
Place the vase on the desk, centered with the legs of the chair you can see beneath the desk.
Turn around, walk past the open doorway, and continue to the white shelves in the wall.
Pick up the blue vase from the bottom shelf.
Turn around and carry the blue vase to the black desk.
Place the blue vase on the desk between the remote control and gold vase.
anns.task_desc: Move two vases to the black desk.

high_descs: move to the coffee table in the middle of the room
pick up a vase from the table
move to the black desk behind you
put the vase on the desk
move to the shelf to the right
pick up a vase from the shelf
move to the black desk behind you
put the vase on the desk
anns.task_desc: Put two different vases on the black desk.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the glass coffee table.
Pick up the gold vase, which is the object closest to you, from the table.
Turn and move to stand in front of the black desk.
Place the vase on the desk to the right of the remote control.
Turn right and move to the white shelves in the wall by the open doorway.
Pick up the blue vase from the bottom shelf.
Turn around and take the blue vase back to the black desk and stand in front of where the gold vase was previously placed.
Place the blue vase on the desk between the remote control and gold vase.
anns.task_desc: Move the two vases to the black desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to face the living room table.
Pick up the candle holder on the living room table.
Turn to the right and walk forward and then turn right to face the computer desk.
Place the candle holder on the computer desk.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the left end of the shelves on the wall.
Pick up the blue candle holder on the bottom shelf.
Turn around and walk around the left side of the computer desk, then turn right and face it.
Place the blue candle holder to the left of the original candle holder.
anns.task_desc: Move two candle holders to the computer desk.
